---
title: Quick Teriyaki Beef & Slaw Tacos with Crispy Shallots & Garlic Aioli
description: Sweet and savoury beef is the star of this crowd-pleasing meal. Easy and satisfying, the tacos come together in a snap, with lots of veggies for everyone to build their own and join in the fun!
